OL,3,CParents sob in court as teenagers
OL,4,Cappear over murder of 16-year-old Chloe
OL,6,FThe parents of three teenagers accused
OL,7,Fof murdering a 16-year-old girl in
OL,8,FLeeds sobbed in court on Tuesday as
OL,9,Fthey appeared before magistrates.
OL,11,FChloe Watson Dransfield died after
OL,12,Fbeing found with stab wounds at
OL,13,FKennerleigh Avenue shortly before 6am
OL,14,Fon Saturday.
OL,16,FWest Yorkshire Police have since
OL,17,Fcharged three young people with her
OL,18,Fmurder, who made a first appearance at
OL,19,FLeeds Magistrates Court on Tuesday
OL,20,Fmorning.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/8
