PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775070658
OL,3,CParents sob in court as teenagers
OL,4,Cappear over murder of 16-year-old Chloe
OL,6,FKayla Smith, 18, Archie Rycroft, 19,
OL,7,Fand a 17-year-old boy who cannot be
OL,8,Fnamed due to his age, are all charged
OL,9,Fwith murder over Chloe's death.
OL,11,FThey appeared for the short hearing in
OL,12,Fgrey, prison-issued tracksuits,
OL,13,Fflanked by security officers.
OL,15,FFamily members of the defendants sat
OL,16,Fin the public gallery visibly upset as
OL,17,Fthey were produced.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775070658
OL,3,CParents sob in court as teenagers
OL,4,Cappear over murder of 16-year-old Chloe
OL,6,FSmith and Rycroft were remanded back
OL,7,Finto custody, while the 17-year-old
OL,8,Fwas remanded into secure accommodation
OL,9,Funtil their next hearing at Leeds
OL,10,FCrown Court on Thursday.
OL,12,FDistrict Judge Mark Daley told them:
OL,13,F"You are all charged with murder. That
OL,14,Fcan only be tried at the crown court,
OL,15,Fand only the crown court can decide
OL,16,Fwhether to grant you bail or not.
OL,18,F"Therefore there has to be a hearing
OL,19,Fat the crown court very soon. That
OL,20,Fwill be on Thursday April 2."
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@AOU|D@]O]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
