PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775070658
OL,3,CParents sob in court as teenagers
OL,4,Cappear over murder of 16-year-old Chloe
OL,6,FNo pleas on the murder charges were
OL,7,Findicated during the hearing.
OL,9,FChloe, from Gomersal, was taken to
OL,10,Fhospital following the incident on
OL,11,FKennerleigh Avenue on Saturday morning
OL,12,Fbut died shortly later.
OL,14,FTwo further teenagers, an 18-year-old
OL,15,Fman and 17-year-old girl, have also
OL,16,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,17,Fand bailed pending further inquiries.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/8
