OL,3,CParents sob in court as teenagers
OL,4,Cappear over murder of 16-year-old Chloe
OL,6,FOn Monday evening, Chloe's father and
OL,7,Fother family members issued a tribute,
OL,8,Fsaying they were "utterly devastated"
OL,9,Fand she would "never be forgotten".
OL,11,F"We miss every single thing about her.
OL,12,FShe was beautiful, full of joy, and
OL,13,Fhad a wonderfully cheeky personality,"
OL,14,Fthey said.
OL,16,F"She embraced life with such
OL,17,Fhappiness, and she had her whole
OL,18,Ffuture ahead of her. Chloe was loved
OL,19,Fby everyone who knew her, and the
OL,20,Fabsence she leaves behind is
OL,21,Fimmeasurable.
OL,26,@pD@ROUpD@eO]qD@OOUqD@bO]sD@AOUuD@fO]xD@
OL,26,AAOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
