OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775070658
OL,3,CParents sob in court as teenagers
OL,4,Cappear over murder of 16-year-old Chloe
OL,6,F"We will miss her forever, she will
OL,7,Fnever be forgotten."
OL,9,FIn a separate tribute, Chloe's mother
OL,10,Fsaid she "cannot put into words" the
OL,11,Floss of her "beautiful princess".
OL,13,F"You are my life, my world, my best
OL,14,Ffriend and I know that I am yours. I
OL,15,Fcannot live without you ` I need you.
OL,17,F"You are stunning, confident, loyal,
OL,18,Fhonest and my family-oriented princess.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@JOUrD@`O]sD@MOUsD@`O]uD@AOUyD@
OL,26,AAOU
