CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1775070658
OL,3,CParents sob in court as teenagers
OL,4,Cappear over murder of 16-year-old Chloe
OL,6,F"When you walk into any room it lights
OL,7,Fup with your bubbly personality. There
OL,8,Fis so much I could say. There's a big
OL,9,Fhole in my heart that can never be
OL,10,Ffilled.
OL,12,F"Your two sisters and big brother will
OL,13,Falways love and miss you to infinity.
OL,14,FYou will always and forever be in our
OL,15,Fhearts."
OL,17,FFlowers were laid in the quiet street
OL,18,Fof bungalows and scenes-of-crime
OL,19,Fofficers in white protective clothing
OL,20,Fwere seen going into one of the homes
OL,21,Fon Monday.
